This Jumbo's location is on 116 street between Lenox and Adam Clayton Powell blvd. (7th ave).  Obviously by the name this place sells burgers but they also serve all day breakfast.  The prices are very reasonable (no more than $10.00 for a meal for one), the location is well kept, and they deliver (without an app).  Would definitely recommend for a quick bite or some breakfast food.
